items.badge_description: Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 205 distinct venues!

Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, there’s a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 80 different venues categorized as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 17!
One cannot live on dank hops alone. Tone down the bitterness and enjoy some smooth flavor. That's 80 different beers with an IBU of 20 or below. Try 5 more for Level 17!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 230 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 47!
99 bottles of beer on the wall, 99 bottles of beer. Take one down, pass it around.... That's 205 checkins with the serving style of Bottle. Try 5 more for Level 42!
